71
00:07:14,897 --> 00:07:16,882
Do you have all your
paperwork done for tomorrow?

72
00:07:16,882 --> 00:07:18,126
Yup.

73
00:07:18,728 --> 00:07:19,887
Things do look good.

74
00:07:19,887 --> 00:07:22,390
Yeah, it looks great.

75
00:07:22,649 --> 00:07:25,469
