We left off yesterday page 38.
1862. The Civil War.

109
00:10:54,274 --> 00:10:57,270
Battlefield medicine.
Clara Barton.

110
00:10:57,286 --> 00:10:59,871
Check out the lipstick on freaky girl.

111
